      "writtenOn": "2021-09-10T20:53:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Looking at this I wonder: do we want to make this field more descriptive? Do we ever expect this to not be a path? Should we just call it path? Or do we want to keep the ability to make it something else in the future?",
