      "writtenOn": "2021-09-10T21:02:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I thought about that a little bit. Making it a label makes sense for cases where the BPF or text-filters are generated at runtime and might not actually exist as a file. There aren\u0027t examples of this yet, so I would be ok with changing it from label to path.",
